items.description:
Applicable to domestic service including lighting, heating, cooking, and power or a combination thereof in a
multifamily accommodation on a single premises where all of the single-family accommodations are separately sub-metered.

*Rate D - Applicable when the customer is entitled to the additional lifeline allowances for both electric water and space heating.
*Power Cost Adjustment $0.015
*Environmental Mitigation Adjustment $0.015 

*The first 395 kWh (During the months of May through October) shall be multiplied by the number of single-family accommodations on the meters.
*The first 670 kWh (During the months of November through April) shall be multiplied by the number of single-family accommodations on the meters.
items.energycomments: Electric Space Heating - November 1 through April 30.
